ttp://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/PARKS-Interior-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1759,8,'2020-01-24 16:41:24','2020-01-24 16:41:24','','PARKS-2','','inherit','open','closed','','parks-2','','','2020-01-24 16:41:24','2020-01-24 16:41:24','',1751,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/PARKS-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1760,8,'2020-01-24 16:42:04','2020-01-24 16:42:04','','PARKS-3','','inherit','open','closed','','parks-3','','','2020-01-24 16:42:04','2020-01-24 16:42:04','',1751,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/PARKS-3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1761,8,'2020-01-25 00:20:36','2020-01-25 00:20:36','<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":35} -->\n<div style=\"height:35px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drive five hours north from New York City and you’ll arrive in Lake Placid.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tucked into the Adirondacks, its small size (just over 2,000 people live in the village) belies the scale of Lake Placid’s sporting history. Host to two Winter Olympics, the area has been drawing skiers, skaters, and more since 1900.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":35} -->\n<div style=\"height:35px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[1762,1763]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1762\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-1/\" class=\"wp-image-1762\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1763\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-2/\" class=\"wp-image-1763\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Photographer Michael Clarke grew up there. Last weekend, he took us back to his hometown with a group of his friends to eat, drink, and play a game of pick-up.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1764,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":900,\"height\":600} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1764\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our goal was Lower Cascade Lake, where Michael and his friends have been skating for years; they visit as often as possible to reconnect and get back in nature.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[1766,1765,1767]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1766\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-5/\" class=\"wp-image-1766\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1765\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-4/\" class=\"wp-image-1765\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1767\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-6/\" class=\"wp-image-1767\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There aren’t a lot of rules in pond hockey, and no one really keeps score. <br><br>Discarded shoes are good enough for goal markers, and picking sides involves throwing your sticks down in a pile. Divide the pile in two, and you’ve got your teams. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1768,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":900,\"height\":600} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1768\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the depths of winter, it’s the perfect opportunity to get your blood pumping and have some fun outside. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[1769,1770]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1769\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-8/\" class=\"wp-image-1769\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1770\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/pond-hockey-9/\" class=\"wp-image-1770\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A few hours later, the game wound down: it was time to eat. Everyone pulled to and got the fire going to cook up tomato soup, sausages, oysters, and crab.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":40} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:metaslider/slider {\"slideshowId\":1777} -->\n<div class=\"alignnormal\">[metaslider id=1777 cssclass=\"\"]</div>\n<!-- /wp:metaslider/slider -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After a few nips of whiskey for warmth, a pleasant weariness sunk in —&nbsp;the kind that only comes from a day well-spent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1774,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":900,\"height\":600} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Pond-Hockey-13.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1774\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->','Pick-Up: An Adventure on Ice','','publish','open','o