49','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slider&#038;p=1536',0,'ml-slider','',0),(614,7,'2019-11-01 01:10:28','2019-11-01 01:10:28','','Slider 602 - image','','publish','closed','closed','','slider-602-image-4','','','2019-11-01 01:14:27','2019-11-01 01:14:27','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slide&#038;p=614',0,'ml-slide','',0),(615,7,'2019-11-01 01:10:28','2019-11-01 01:10:28','','Slider 602 - image','','publish','closed','closed','','slider-602-image-5','','','2019-11-01 01:14:27','2019-11-01 01:14:27','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slide&#038;p=615',1,'ml-slide','',0),(1416,8,'2019-11-21 20:03:40','2019-11-21 20:03:40','','American Woolen Feature','','inherit','open','closed','','american-woolen-feature','','','2019-11-21 20:03:40','2019-11-21 20:03:40','',1414,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/American-Woolen-Feature.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1718,8,'2020-01-15 16:59:28','2020-01-15 16:59:28','<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":40} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When temperatures really start to drop, we always turn to <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/best-down\">down</a>. Lightweight, compressible, and incredibly warm, it\'s our top choice in bitter weather. Thankfully, it doesn’t require much care to keep down working in peak condition all winter long. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-default\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":40} -->\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>DOWN CARE TIPS</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><strong>Spot clean</strong> whenever you can. <br><br></li><li>If you spot loose feathers, the fabric in your piece is likely torn — <strong>repair it using a needle and thread</strong>, in a color that matches the stitching on the item. <br><br></li><li>Try to <strong><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/down-repel-spray\">keep your down dry</a></strong> as much as possible. If it does get wet, make sure to let it air out before storing it, to prevent mold from developing. </li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The goal with <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/best-down\">down</a> is to keep the feathers as lofty as possible; it’s the air between them that traps heat and keeps you warm. Washing down helps restore the loft to compressed feathers. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":55} -->\n<div style=\"height:55px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>HOW TO WASH YOUR DOWN</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":35} -->\n<div style=\"height:35px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Comforters and sleeping bags don’t need to be washed more than every other year or so, but your <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/best-down\">outdoor gear</a> may need more frequent care. Take note: improper washing can actually damage or shrink the down insulation, which is why it’s important to use <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/down-wash-kit\">the right products</a> and follow a few key rules. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>First things first: always check the care instructions provided by the manufacturer. <br><br></li><li>When washing down, use the <strong>largest possible front-loading washing machine</strong><em> </em>you can find. <em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Do</span></em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> </span><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">not</span></em> use a top-loading machine. <br><br></li><li>Pour a 50ml capful of <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/down-wash-kit\">Down Wash</a> per one large item or two smaller items (a half cap is fine if you’re handwashing) directly into your detergent drawer. If you don’t have <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/down-wash-kit\">Down Wash</a>, use very gentle detergent; harsh products will strip the feathers of their natural oils. <br><br></li><li>Wash your piece on a full cycle at 30°C/86°F, or according to its care label instructions. Always use cold or mild water, <em>never</em> hot. Sometimes you may need to do an extra rinse cycle, without detergent, to ensure everything is washed out — otherwise, the feathers will be weighed down by product and won’t return to their maximum loft. <br><br></li><li>Once washed, check that the down is evenly distributed throughout your piece. <br><br></li><li>Dry on a low, gentle, or delicate cycle with <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/down-wash-kit\">down dryer balls</a>, tennis balls, or wool balls. The goal is to “beat up” the down, to help it fluff back up. Additionally, you should periodically check your product while it’s drying and give it a fluff by hand. <br><br></li><li>It may take a few cycles, but be patient. Once your piece is fully dry, you’re good to go! </li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In jackets, sleeping bags, comforters, and more <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/best-down\">down</a> works hard to keep us warm all winter long. Make sure your gear is always ready to perform with the right care. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->','How-To: Down Care','','publish','open','open','','how-to-down-care','','','2020-01-15 16:59:29','2020-01-15 16:59:29','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?p=1718',0,'post','',0),(1351,8,'2019-11-14 21:54:22','2019-11-14 21:54:22','','Slider 1348 - image','','publish','closed','closed','','slider-1348-image-2','','','2019-11-14 21:54:38','2019-11-14 21:54:38','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slide&#038;p=1351',1,'ml-slide','',0),(1352,8,'2019-11-14 21:54:35','2019-11-14 21:54:35','','Slider 1348 - image','','publish','closed','closed','','slider-1348-image-3','','','2019-11-14 21:54:38','2019-11-14 21:54:38','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slide&#038;p=1352',2,'ml-slide','',0),(1353,8,'2019-11-14 21:54:45','2019-11-14 21:54:45','','Svalbard 3A','','publish','closed','closed','','new-slideshow-16','','','2019-11-14 21:55:45','2019-11-14 21:55:45','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=ml-slider&#038;p=1353',0,'ml-slider','',0),(707,8,'2019-11-05 20:51:05','2019-11-05 20:51:05','','The Famous Red Wool Pullover','','publish','closed','closed','','the-famous-red-wool-pullover','','','2019-11-05 20:51:05','2019-11-05 20:51:05','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=707',0,'product','',0),(708,8,'2019-11-0