om/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Bavaria_Farm9.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1491,8,'2019-12-03 17:44:13','2019-12-03 17:44:13','','Bavaria_Farm10','','inherit','open','closed','','bavaria_farm10','','','2019-12-03 17:44:13','2019-12-03 17:44:13','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Bavaria_Farm10.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1492,8,'2019-12-03 17:44:14','2019-12-03 17:44:14','','Bavaria_Farm11','','inherit','open','closed','','bavaria_farm11','','','2019-12-03 17:44:14','2019-12-03 17:44:14','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Bavaria_Farm11.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1493,8,'2019-12-03 17:44:15','2019-12-03 17:44:15','','Bavaria_Farm12','','inherit','open','closed','','bavaria_farm12','','','2019-12-03 17:44:15','2019-12-03 17:44:15','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Bavaria_Farm12.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1494,8,'2019-12-03 17:44:16','2019-12-03 17:44:16','','Bavaria_Farm13','','inherit','open','closed','','bavaria_farm13','','','2019-12-03 17:44:16','2019-12-03 17:44:16','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Bavaria_Farm13.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1162,8,'2019-11-14 17:39:48','2019-11-14 17:39:48','','MallmannsProvence18','','inherit','open','closed','','mallmannsprovence18','','','2019-11-14 17:39:48','2019-11-14 17:39:48','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MallmannsProvence18.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1124,8,'2019-11-14 16:36:04','2019-11-14 16:36:04','','MallmannsProvence3','','inherit','open','closed','','mallmannsprovence3','','','2019-11-14 16:36:04','2019-11-14 16:36:04','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MallmannsProvence3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1414,8,'2019-11-26 18:47:46','2019-11-26 18:47:46','<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Located</strong>: Stafford Springs, CT<br><strong>Founded</strong>: 1899<br><strong>Type of Business</strong>: Woolen Mill</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once the world’s largest wool manufacturer, the American Woolen Company is an iconic name in the history of American textiles. They were the clear choice when we began searching for a partner to help develop exceptional custom woolen fabrics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Their history traces back to 1853, when Warren Mills was founded in Stafford Springs, CT — it was the start of the second Industrial Revolution, and manufacturing in New England was booming. Further north and nearly half a century later, the American Woolen Company (AWC) itself was founded in Lawrence, MA.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[1418,1417]} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/American-Woolen-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1418\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?attachment_id=1418\" class=\"wp-image-1418\"/></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/American-Woolen-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1417\" data-link=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?attachment_id=1417\" class=\"wp-image-1417\"/></figure></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In pursuit of creating the best possible fabrics, AWC purchased the historic Warren Mills in 1925. At the time, it was the only U.S. mill capable of producing the highest qualities of both worsted and woolen cloth.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1420,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":675,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/American-Woolen-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1420\" width=\"675\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Today, AWC is leading a new textile design movement committed to preserving the craft and defining an authentic American style. Their products pass through three phases and 13 highly meticulous steps to go from fiber to yarn, yarn to fabric, and fabric to garment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1419,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":675,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/American-Woolen-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1419\" width=\"675\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All of their employees are 3rd- and 4th-generation workers with roots in the Northeast, who are dedicated to creating a superior product at every step of the process. Their skill, knowledge, and attention to detail are unparalleled. Today, the American Woolen Mill is producing some of the finest fabrics in the world and defining a new aesthetic that celebrates centuries of New England craftsmanship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->','Our Makers: American Woolen Company','','publish','open','open','','american-woolen-company','','','2019-12-03 21:24:05','2019-12-03 21:24:05','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?p=1414',0,'post','',0),(1380,7,'2019-11-14 22:34:13','2019-11-14 22:34:13','','The Canvas Camp Stool','','publish','closed','closed','','the-canvas-camp-stool','','','2019-11-14 22:34:13','2019-11-14 22:34:13','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=1380',0,'product','',0),(1381,8,'2019-11-14 22:33:57','2019-11-14 22:33:57','','Sam McGee Feature','','inherit','open','closed','','sam-mcgee-feature','','','2019-11-14 22:33:57','2019-11-14 22:33:57','',478,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Sam-McGee-Feature.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1382,7,'2019-11-14 22:34:04','2019-11-14 22:34:04','','1468954720','','inherit','open','closed','','1468954720','','','2019-11-14 22:34:04','2019-11-14 22:34:04','',1380,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/1468954720.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1384,7,'2019-11-14 22:35:21','2019-11-14 22:35:21','','The Coated Canvas Tote','','publish','closed','closed','','the-coated-canvas-tote','','','2019-11-14 22:35:21','2019-11-14 22:35:21','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=1384',0,'product','',0),(1385,7,'2019-11-14 22:35:03','2019-11-14 22:35:03','','bmc_061318_canvas_tote_large_0010_GW_MG','','inherit','open','closed','','bmc_061318_canvas_tote_large_0010_gw_mg','','','2019-11-14 22:35:03','2019-11-14 22:35:03','',1384,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/bmc_061318_canvas_tote_large_0010_GW_MG.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1748,8,'2020-01-22 19:42:30','2020-01-22 19:42:30','','Wool & Cashmere Shampoo','','publish','closed','closed','','wool-cashmere-shampoo','','','2020-01-22 19:42:30','2020-01-22 19:42:30','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=1748',0,'product','',0),(1749,8,'2020-01-22 19:42:23','2020-01-22 19:42:23','','Wool Shampoo','','inherit','open','closed','','wool-shampoo','','','2020-01-22 19:42:23','2020-01-22 19:42:23','',1748,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Wool-Shampoo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1388,8,'2019-11-14 22:37:42','2019-11-14 22:37:42','<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Camping is an American tradition. It\'s a chance to get away from the mundane and tap into the more fundamental elements of life. From the seasoned outdoor adventurer to the greenhorn, everyone can benefit from hitting the trail and getting outside their own head for a bit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On any adventure, it\'s important to keep in mind the always applicable Scout motto: be prepared. To that end, we’ve pulled together a must-have checklist to help you tackle your next camping trip in confidence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1267,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Haves-Osprey-Backpack.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1267\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>1. Backpack</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First thing\'s first — get something to carry your gear in. The right backpack can make or break a camping trip, especially if you\'re planning long treks.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The length of your trip dictates how big of a pack you\'ll need; if you\'re hiking to your next camping spot, your backpack must be able to hold all your gear. A good fit is essential: keep your mind on the trail, not constant readjustments. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.backpacker.com/gear/backpack-buying-guide\">A little research</a> goes a long way towards finding the perfect backpack — but if you\'re looking for a solid pack that can handle anything from a one-night camp to a five-day hike, check out Osprey, known for their trustworthy, durable bags.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.osprey.com/us/en/product/aether-ag-60-AETHER60_807.html\"><strong>Osprey Aether AG 60</strong></a><strong>, $290</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1266,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Haves-Marmot-Tent.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1266\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>2. Tent</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When shopping for a tent, consider how many people will be sleeping in it on average — because it\'s an investment, think about what your next few years of camping might look like, not just the next trip.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take into account what kind of camping you\'re planning on. Something breathable but waterproof is good enough for the summer, but if you\'re heading out in winter you\'ll want to upgrade to a four-season tent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The rest is up to personal preference. Tent styles are varied, and each comes equipped with its own set of features. If you want an all-around cover-your-bases tent, we always trust Marmot. The Marmot Limestone 4P is versatile, fitting up to four people — though you\'ll want something smaller if you\'re backpacking it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.rei.com/product/110892/marmot-limestone-4p-tent?cm_mmc=aff_AL-_-38931-_-52463-_-NA&amp;avad=52463_d16e23b41\"><strong>Marmot Limestone 4P Tent</strong></a><strong>, $359</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":897,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":450,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Hobo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-897\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>3. Hobo Knife</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A sturdy multitool can save a lot of space on the trail. With a sleek folding design, a single hobo knife can replace the clutter of various eating utensils. Standard versions include a knife, fork, and spoon, and are easy to stow in your pack.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These all-in-one knives got their start during the Great Depression, and are still valuable tools today.&nbsp; We humbly suggest our own <a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/branded-hobo-knife?taxon_id=1493\">Hobo Knife</a> for your next trip: durable and sleek, it disassembles when you want access to all three utensils and easily snaps back together. Plus, it comes with a bottle opener —&nbsp;something you\'re bound to appreciate at the end of a long day outdoors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/branded-hobo-knife?taxon_id=1493\"><strong>The Hobo Knife</strong></a><strong>, $48</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1261,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":450,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Have-Field-Skillet.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1261\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>4. Cast Iron Skillet</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Is it really a camping trip without a hot breakfast straight out of the skillet? Maybe — but not one we want to be on.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bringing along a good cast iron skillet can fundamentally change a camping experience. It lets you ditch trail mix in favor of real meals, and cast iron only gets better with age and use —&nbsp;as long you <a href=\"https://fieldcompany.com/pages/how-to-clean-maintain-cast-iron-pan-skillet\">properly maintain it</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Field #10 Cast Iron Skillet is our number one choice. It\'s pre-seasoned, has a nonstick surface, weighs only 6 lbs, and is American-made. It\'s not likely to make it on your next long-distance trek, but for basic camping, it\'s invaluable. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/field-10-cast-iron-skillet?taxon_id=1493\"><strong>The Field #10 Cast Iron Skillet</strong></a><strong>, $160</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/leather-pot-handle?taxon_id=1493\"><strong>The Leather Pot Handle</strong></a><strong>, $22</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1264,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":450,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Have-Seamless-Mug.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1264\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>5. Enamelware</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The blue-and-white-speckled dishes and pots that seem ubiquitous on camping trips are more than just nostalgic.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Enamelware is lightweight, durable, and fireproof — in other words, easy to carry around and hard to damage. Made from thin steel with glass particles fused to the outside, enamelware lasts longer than glass or ceramic dishware. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shelves these days are stacked with all sorts of enamelware, some better than others. The Best Made Seamless &amp; Steadfast Enamelware Collection is designed to withstand the worst, double-dipped using WWII-era techniques for a level of quality and craftsmanship you’re unlikely to find anywhere else.&nbsp; Start off with a couple of tumblers for drinks by the fire, or get your whole outdoor dinner setup in one go.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/seamless-steadfast-enamel-cups?option_values=5146&amp;taxon_id=1586\"><strong>Seamless &amp; Steadfast Enamel Cups</strong></a><strong>, $36</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/seamless-steadfast-enamel-bowls?option_values=5150&amp;taxon_id=1586\"><strong>Seamless &amp; Steadfast Enamel Bowls</strong></a><strong>, $46</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/seamless-steadfast-enamel-utility-pot?taxon_id=1586\"><strong>Seamless &amp; Steadfast Enamel Utility Pot</strong></a><strong>, $52</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":30} -->\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":785,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/REISleepingBag-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-785\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>6. Sleeping Bag</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are lightweight sleeping bags for the summer and heavy-duty ones for the winter. There are square ones and body-shaped ones that zip up past your face aptly called mummy bags. Much like a tent, your choice of sleeping bag depends largely on personal preference and the type of camping you expect to be doing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most important part of any sleeping bag is how warm it keeps you — which is why, typically, they come with temperature ratings. Research the weather of the place you\'re going to camp, or if you plan on camping throughout the year go for a three-season bag.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To cover the most bases, we recommend the REI Co-op Magma 15 sleeping bag. It’s lightweight, insulated, compresses for easy packing, and has a 16-degree temperature rating.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.rei.com/product/148248/rei-co-op-magma-15-sleeping-bag-mens?cm_mmc=aff_AL-_-145262-_-180150-_-NA&amp;avad=180150_f16e32e31\"><strong>REI Co-op Magma 15 Sleeping Bag</strong></a><strong>, $258 - $273</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1263,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":450,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Have-Mini-Flashlight.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1263\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>7. Flashlight</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Moonless nights, midnight bathroom trips, early morning departures...whatever the occasion, it’s best to bring along a flashlight to illuminate the way. Keep one in the car on your way to the campground or trailhead and one in your pack at all times — you never know when it might come in handy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For a sturdy flashlight that won\'t quit on you when you need it the most, go with a strong (but not too big) shell. The Best Made Brass Flashlight Mini ML-X is the size of a shotgun shell, but it holds more than enough power to fool anyone at the other end. It\'s small, long-lasting, and a smart tool to have in the arsenal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/brass-flashlight-mini-ml-x?taxon_id=1493\"><strong>The Brass Flashlight: Mini ML-X</strong></a><strong>, $118</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":787,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pad.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-787\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>8. Sleeping Pads</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is optional (and many camping purists avoid it), but it can provide a lot of relief when sleeping on rough terrain. After all, a good night’s rest is a requisite for facing whatever the next day brings.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you\'re looking to embark on a multi-day backpacking trip, consider an inflatable one that you can roll up and stash, or get a folding foam pad that straps easily to the outside of your pack to avoid worrying about punctures. If you\'re going straight from the car to the campground you can opt for something heavier, like a self-inflating pad.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Personally, we like foam pads: they\'re lightweight, inexpensive, and very durable (though not quite as comfortable as their air mattress-like counterparts). The Therm-a-Rest Z Lite Sol Sleeping Pad is a great choice that does the trick, folds up, and is easy to cut to size.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.rei.com/product/829826/therm-a-rest-z-lite-sol-sleeping-pad?cm_mmc=aff_AL-_-3184-_-3816-_-NA&amp;avad=3816_c12c97da9\"><strong>Therm-a-Rest Z Lite Sol Sleeping Pad</strong></a><strong>, $26 - $34</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1262,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":450,\"height\":450} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Camping-Must-Have-Merino.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1262\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>9. Merino Baselayers</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being out in the elements can take a lot out of you — wearing proper, versatile clothing is key to staying comfortable. When we say versatile, we mean something that will keep you in a reliable middle ground, neither too hot nor too cold.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Go for pieces made with merino wool: it\'s proven to regulate temperature, wick away moisture, and is antimicrobial, too. Plus, it\'s exceptionally comfortable and soft. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>From long johns to boxer briefs to tees, our merino wool pieces are designed to sit close to your body without squeezing or chafing and are constructed to maintain their shape over years of wear.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/merino-boxer-brief?option_values=7461\"><strong>The Merino Boxer Brief</strong></a><strong>, $58</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/merino-long-johns?option_values=7415\"><strong>The Merino Long Johns</strong></a><strong>, $98</strong><br><a href=\"https://www.bestmadeco.com/products/long-sleeve-merino-tee?option_values=7407\"><strong>The Long-Sleeve Merino Tee</strong></a><strong>, $118</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":789,\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":356,\"height\":550} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img src=\"https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Nalgene.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-789\" width=\"356\" height=\"550\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>10. Canteen</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Canteens, hydro flasks, water bottles — whatever you call them, you need one. Basic but essential, they’re required for any trip or hike into the wilderness; it\'s important to stay hydrated. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Some strap onto a backpack, some backpacks come with a hydration system with a drinking tube, some bottles have straws, some are wide-mouthed reservoirs, and some are insulated. Whatever you choose, just don’t forget to bring it along. Personally, we like the simplicity of the classic Nalgene. It\'s BPA-free, indestructible, and it gets our water from point A to point B with minimal fuss.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.nalgene.com/product/2178-2040/\"><strong>Nalgene 32-oz Wide Mouth Water Bottle</strong></a><strong>, $11.54</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With these 10 items you can rest assured that your camping trip will go off without a serious hitch — but don’t forget to think beyond the essentials. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Books, pen and paper, board games, pillows, blankets, cards, a flask — pack whatever will help you enjoy your time outdoors. Camping reminds us of what we love, whether it\'s spending time with friends and family or enjoying the solitude of nature and pride in a good day’s work.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->','Our 10 Camping Must-Haves','','inherit','closed','closed','','762-autosave-v1','','','2019-11-14 22:37:42','2019-11-14 22:37:42','',762,'https://editorial.bestmadeco.com/uncategorized/762-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1643,8,'2019-12-13 16:23:10','2019-12-13 16:23:10','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Friggatriskaidekaphobia</em> (the fear of Friday the Thirteenth) is believed to be a combination of two separate superstitions: that of Friday the 13th being an unlucky day, and the belief that 13 itself is an unlucky number.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The unluckiness of sailors is well documented, as are their superstitions&nbsp;— many would refuse to begin a voyage on a Friday. The urban myth of the 19th-century ship&nbsp;<em>HMS Friday</em>&nbsp;is a prime example. As the story goes, in an effort to dispel the superstition of sailing on Fridays and the unluckiness of the number thirteen, the Royal Navy built a ship dubbed the&nbsp;<em>HMS Friday</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Her keel was laid on a Friday; she was launched on a Friday; christened on a Friday; set out on her maiden voyage on Friday the thirteenth; crewed by thirteen;&nbsp;captained by James Friday...and was subsequently never seen again.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>But that story was a lie, gotten up by some bumboat man to frighten superstitious people.</p><cite>S. Grant Smith, in an address delivered at Coney Island, 1895</cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Quote taken from the&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://t.umblr.com/redirect?z=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DIxZiAAAAMAAJ%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%26dq%3DAnnual%2BReport%2BOf%2BThe%2BOfficers%2BOf%2BThe%2BThirteen%2BClub%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ei%3D-h4yUpq_AqOO2wX5g4DwBg%26ved%3D0CEEQ6AEwAA%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&amp;t=MjM5MDFiYmRkNjMxN2Q2N2QyN2Y3N2VjMTE0ZTgwYjVmNjZjNjNhYyw3TWNrV3Vxcw%3D%3D&amp;b=t%3A4hMU0CtHQrpf0AuPrck0dg&amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fbestmadeco.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F61112320156%2Ffriday-the-thirteenth-a-commonly-held-theory-of&amp;m=1\" target=\"_blank\">Fourteenth Annual Report of the Officers of the Thirteen Club, January 13th, 1896</a></em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":50} -->\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->','Friggatriskaidekaphobia','','publish','open','open','','friggatriskaidekaphobia','','','2019-12-13 16:23:12','2019-12-13 16:23:12','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/?p=1643',0,'post','',0),(1644,8,'2019-12-12 19:57:01','2019-12-12 19:57:01','','Friday13thFeature','','inherit','open','closed','','friday13thfeature','','','2019-12-12 19:57:01','2019-12-12 19:57:01','',1643,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Friday13thFeature.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1645,8,'2019-12-12 19:57:20','2019-12-12 19:57:20','','Friday13thThumbnail','','inherit','open','closed','','friday13ththumbnail','','','2019-12-12 19:57:20','2019-12-12 19:57:20','',1643,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Friday13thThumbnail.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1666,8,'2019-12-13 17:14:57','2019-12-13 17:14:57','','Ice Fishing 13','','inherit','open','closed','','ice-fishing-13','','','2019-12-13 17:14:57','2019-12-13 17:14:57','',0,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Ice-Fishing-13.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1667,8,'2019-12-13 17:35:56','2019-12-13 17:35:56','','Fried Rice Feature','','inherit','open','closed','','fried-rice-feature','','','2019-12-13 17:35:56','2019-12-13 17:35:56','',1647,'http://editorial.bestmadeco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Fried-Rice-Feature.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1668,8,'2019-12-13 17:36:35','2019-12-13 17:36:35','','Fried Rice Thumbnail','','inherit','open','closed','','fried-rice-thumbnail','','','2019-12-13 17:36:35','2019-12-13 17:36:35','',1647,'http://editorial.be